│ 6a. Simplified recipe format                                                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ The agent provides a compact "recipe" JSON. The system expands it into the full internal types.                                               │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ {                                                                                                                                             │
│   "protocol": "uniswap-v3",                                                                                                                   │
│   "primitive": "swap",                                                                                                                        │
│   "chain_id": 8453,                                                                                                                           │
│   "template_id": "exact-input-single",                                                                                                        │
│   "contracts": [                                                                                                                              │
│     {                                                                                                                                         │
│       "role": "router",                                                                                                                       │
│       "address": "0x2626664c2603336E57B271c5C0b26F421741e481",                                                                                │
│       "abi_json": "[{\"type\":\"function\",\"name\":\"exactInputSingle\",...}]",                                                              │
│       "source_ref": "https://basescan.org/address/0x2626..."                                                                                  │
│     }                                                                                                                                         │
│   ],                                                                                                                                          │
│   "actions": [                                                                                                                                │
│     {                                                                                                                                         │
│       "action_id": "swap_exact_in",                                                                                                           │
│       "calls": [                                                                                                                              │
│         { "role": "router", "function": "exactInputSingle" }                                                                                  │
│       ],                                                                                                                                      │
│       "postconditions": ["output_amount_above_minimum"]                                                                                       │
│     }                                                                                                                                         │
│   ],                                                                                                                                          │
│   "max_value_wei_per_call": "1000000000000000000",                                                                                            │
│   "template_budget_wei": "10000000000000000000"                                                                                               │
│ }                                                                                                                                             │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ Key simplifications vs current StrategyTemplate:                                                                                              │
│ - No version (removed in step 4)                                                                                                              │
│ - No AbiFunctionSpec — the agent just names the function; the system finds it in the ABI                                                      │
│ - No selector_hex, inputs, outputs, state_mutability — extracted from ABI automatically                                                       │
│ - contracts[].abi_json replaces separate ABI artifact ingestion                                                                               │
│ - Budget constraints are top-level fields, not a nested constraints_json blob                                                                 │
│ - preconditions and risk_checks are optional (default to empty)                                                                               │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ 6b. Implementation in src/tools.rs                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ New function: fn register_strategy_tool(args_json: &str) -> Result<String, String>                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ Pipeline:                                                                                                                                     │
│ 1. Parse the recipe JSON into a StrategyRecipe struct (new, defined in tools.rs or a shared location)                                         │
│ 2. For each contract in recipe.contracts:                                                                                                     │
│   - Call abi::normalize_abi_artifact() to parse and validate the raw ABI JSON                                                                 │
│   - Extract functions referenced by the recipe's actions                                                                                      │
│   - Store via registry::upsert_abi_artifact()                                                                                                 │
│ 3. Build a full StrategyTemplate:                                                                                                             │
│   - key from recipe fields                                                                                                                    │
│   - status: TemplateStatus::Draft initially                                                                                                   │
│   - contract_roles from recipe.contracts (role, address, source_ref)                                                                          │
│   - actions from recipe.actions — for each call, match function name to the normalized ABI functions, build AbiFunctionSpec                   │
│   - constraints_json serialized from recipe budget fields, with safe defaults (see 6d)                                                        │
│ 4. Store via registry::upsert_template()                                                                                                      │
│ 5. Run compiler::dry_run_compile(&key) to validate the full path                                                                              │
│ 6. If dry-run passes: auto-activate via registry::set_activation() with enabled: true                                                         │
│ 7. Return the stored template as JSON confirmation                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ 6c. Tool schema in src/features/inference.rs                                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ Add register_strategy tool with descriptive schema. Key properties:                                                                           │
│ - protocol (string, required)                                                                                                                 │
│ - primitive (string, required)                                                                                                                │
│ - chain_id (integer, required)                                                                                                                │
│ - template_id (string, required)                                                                                                              │
│ - contracts (array, required) — each with role, address, abi_json, source_ref                                                                 │
│ - actions (array, required) — each with action_id, calls (array of {role, function}), postconditions                                          │
│ - max_value_wei_per_call (string, optional)                                                                                                   │
│ - template_budget_wei (string, optional)                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ Description should guide the agent: "Register a new strategy template from contract ABIs. Use http_fetch to retrieve ABIs from block          │
│ explorers first. The system validates selectors, runs a dry-run compile, and auto-activates on success."                                      │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ 6d. Safe defaults for agent-created templates                                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ When the recipe omits budget fields, apply conservative defaults:                                                                             │
│ - max_calls: 5                                                                                                                                │
│ - max_value_wei_per_call: "100000000000000000" (0.1 ETH)                                                                                      │
│ - template_budget_wei: "1000000000000000000" (1 ETH lifetime)                                                                                 │
│ - max_total_value_wei: same as max_value_wei_per_call                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                               │
│ These can be overridden by the agent in the recipe, but the defaults prevent unbounded spending.                                              │
│                                                                                                                                               │
